title: Can You Die From Lack of Sleep? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 346
description:
What’s the proper way to recycle? Where do pizza boxes go? And how long can someone go without sleep? On this episode, Rhett and Link are going down the rabbit hole with help of a [not-so] reliable topic generator. What could go wrong? Also, Link’s vacation glasses are back by popular demand! Remember - Summer is temporary, but Drip is forever.
Want to hear your voice on Ear Biscuits? Call 1-888-EAR-POD1 and we might just play your call on an upcoming episode!
